node.text: goes to one fight & thinks she’s a boxer 🤣🥊 #LiteboxerPartner but seriously, @liteboxer is my new favorite workout. I never boxed much before, but they have intro classes that break it down and make it easy to get into! You can also punch to your favorite music or take classes for a full-body workout 💃🏼
